title: Total Pro Golf 3 Patch - SoN
description:
Game: Total Pro Golf 3
Coded: March 4, 2016 by SoN
Type: Patch

Description: Prepare to join the professional golf ranks with Total Pro Golf 3. Create your own golfer on either the American or European tour, play up through the junior ranks to the professional level and then retire off on the senior circuit. Manage your golferâ€™s career with built in RPG style elements while playing out your rounds in a quick and strategic manner using one of two play styles.

Instructions: This is just a basic patch. Install Total Pro Golf 3 as normal. Open the patch as admin. Click the "Browse" button and select the TPG3.exe from the installation folder. Tick the "Make Backup" box if you want to make a backup of the original exe. Click the "Crack" button. If you load a season disk the license screen will pop up, just click the license button without entering a code. It will accept it. That is it. Enjoy!

Notes: "I have said it thrice: What I tell you three times is true." - Lewis Carroll
